WEBVTT

01:32.220 --> 01:34.970
[How dare you!?]

01:35.039 --> 01:38.009
[Episode 15]

01:41.400 --> 01:42.660
How could this happen?

01:42.950 --> 01:45.000
He went straight to bed after he came back

01:45.000 --> 01:46.729
and has been asleep ever since.

01:47.009 --> 01:48.470
He hasn't eaten anything.

01:49.070 --> 01:52.130
Is it still because of the Yan people
entering the city?

01:52.430 --> 01:53.960
News from the frontier says

01:54.759 --> 01:57.120
that since Zhaluowahan,
the Emperor of Yan,

01:57.120 --> 02:00.150
agreed to send an envoy delegation
for Dan's birthday celebration,

02:00.150 --> 02:01.510
it has been half a month.

02:01.710 --> 02:04.040
They still haven't reached an agreement.

02:05.230 --> 02:06.630
I can't enter the court,

02:06.870 --> 02:08.400
so I don't know the details.

02:08.560 --> 02:10.830
Is it the Empress Dowager who opposes it,

02:11.150 --> 02:12.430
or Prince Duan?

02:12.800 --> 02:13.530
Both of them.

02:15.190 --> 02:18.390
It was expected that the Empress Dowager
would oppose it.

02:18.520 --> 02:21.360
After all, if the peace talks succeed
and there's no war,

02:21.360 --> 02:24.160
Prince Duan's troops
won't be tied up at the border

02:24.190 --> 02:26.320
and could instead be used against her.

02:26.960 --> 02:28.090
But we didn't expect

02:28.710 --> 02:32.470
that Prince Duan, perhaps fearing
that the army would be hard to control

02:32.470 --> 02:34.840
if it returned to the capital,
would also be against it.

02:34.840 --> 02:37.100
We still haven't figured out a solution.

02:38.140 --> 02:40.600
These people
claim to care about the nation,

02:41.310 --> 02:43.710
but who cares about Dan's life and safety?

02:44.750 --> 02:46.310
His health is fragile already,

02:46.310 --> 02:48.040
and he suffers from headaches.

02:55.910 --> 02:56.520
Indeed.

02:57.480 --> 03:00.140
These ministers
treat him like a fool every day,

03:01.150 --> 03:04.400
and he has to deal with each of them
while pretending to be one.

03:04.400 --> 03:06.000
I can hide in the Cold Palace,

03:06.360 --> 03:07.710
but where can he hide?

03:09.190 --> 03:11.590
This is the secret letter
Dan brought back.

03:12.730 --> 03:13.390
Take a look.

03:14.750 --> 03:16.550
It was after reading this letter

03:16.680 --> 03:18.610
that his headache flared up again.

03:19.320 --> 03:22.310
[Emperor of Yan is hospitable.
I couldn't refuse his hospitality]

03:20.280 --> 03:22.329
Emperor of Yan is hospitable.
I couldn't refuse his hospitality...

03:22.329 --> 03:24.480
[I'm afraid I'll have to stay here for
a few days and will be late. Wang Zhao]

03:24.950 --> 03:27.410
Wang Zhao
was detained by the Emperor of Yan?

03:31.680 --> 03:32.320
Mr. Bei,

03:33.710 --> 03:35.530
I've been in the Cold Palace
for 2 months now.

03:35.530 --> 03:37.360
I don't need to pay respects
to the Empress Dowager,

03:37.360 --> 03:40.020
and I've been cut off
from Prince Duan's spying.

03:40.310 --> 03:42.640
It's like taking an extremely long leave.

03:46.590 --> 03:48.650
But I can't keep hiding like a coward,

03:49.010 --> 03:51.010
leaving him alone to deal with them.

03:51.360 --> 03:53.220
You want to leave the Cold Palace?

03:53.680 --> 03:54.480
That's right.

03:55.360 --> 03:57.470
But didn't Dan
tell you to wait a little longer

03:57.470 --> 04:00.000
until he finds a reason
for your restoration?

04:03.120 --> 04:04.160
I have to think...

04:06.080 --> 04:07.590
what reason I could use.

04:08.660 --> 04:11.750
[Office of Drums and Bells]

04:11.870 --> 04:13.330
I'm innocent!

04:13.690 --> 04:16.100
[Office of Drums and Bells]

04:14.080 --> 04:16.209
I suffer in this Cold Palace every day,

04:16.680 --> 04:18.390
calling to heaven and earth for help

04:18.390 --> 04:19.510
to no avail!

04:20.000 --> 04:21.720
And the real culprit is out there,

04:21.720 --> 04:23.510
living carefree!

04:26.040 --> 04:26.760
Today,

04:26.970 --> 04:29.960
[Office of Drums and Bells]

04:27.190 --> 04:29.720
I will expose her scheme to the world!

04:30.360 --> 04:32.320
Everyone in the palace,

04:32.750 --> 04:34.480
young and old, girls and maids,

04:34.480 --> 04:36.830
please judge this!

04:38.870 --> 04:39.790
Your Majesty,

04:40.070 --> 04:40.800
I specially prepared

04:40.800 --> 04:43.200
this rose essence for you myself.

04:43.600 --> 04:44.560
After using it,

04:44.630 --> 04:47.450
your skin will be firm,
smooth, and elastic.

04:47.560 --> 04:50.270
-Your Majesty!
-And the fragrance will last...

04:51.240 --> 04:52.830
Your Majesty,

04:52.950 --> 04:56.159
please help me get justice, Your Majesty!

04:56.159 --> 04:57.390
What's going on?

04:57.630 --> 05:00.560
Why are you crying
so early in the morning?

05:00.720 --> 05:02.450
Your Majesty, you have no idea,

05:02.510 --> 05:03.460
but Concubine Yu

05:03.720 --> 05:04.950
has gone mad!

05:05.600 --> 05:07.310
She's been locked in the Cold Palace.

05:07.310 --> 05:09.440
How could she still cause you trouble?

05:09.600 --> 05:10.640
I thought

05:10.800 --> 05:12.460
she would behave from then on,

05:12.600 --> 05:14.530
but this morning she was shouting

05:14.630 --> 05:15.820
and claiming

05:16.040 --> 05:17.630
that I'm the real culprit

05:17.950 --> 05:19.830
and she's the victim.

05:19.920 --> 05:21.320
Are you the real culprit?

05:21.360 --> 05:23.000
I'm not.

05:23.070 --> 05:25.560
So what are you afraid of?

05:26.070 --> 05:27.360
If a mad dog bites you,

05:27.360 --> 05:29.690
are you going to bite it back?

05:30.120 --> 05:32.050
But the things she said were awful.

05:32.070 --> 05:34.190
Now the whole harem is spreading

05:34.240 --> 05:35.680
that she's innocent.

05:35.830 --> 05:38.000
If His Majesty hears this...

05:38.390 --> 05:39.510
Your Majesty!

05:39.630 --> 05:42.720
Please help me get justice, Your Majesty!

05:42.720 --> 05:43.950
Alright, alright.

05:44.390 --> 05:46.270
If the Emperor blames you,

05:46.600 --> 05:49.120
I will certainly stand up for you.

05:49.190 --> 05:49.830
Let's go.

05:52.480 --> 05:53.210
Consort Shu.

05:53.920 --> 05:55.320
The floor is cold. Get up.

06:01.390 --> 06:02.450
What's happening?

06:02.680 --> 06:03.410
She vomited?

06:04.190 --> 06:04.950
Consort Xie.

06:05.680 --> 06:07.800
Hurry up and summon the imperial physician

06:07.800 --> 06:08.950
to check on Consort Xie!

06:08.950 --> 06:09.430
Yes.

06:18.310 --> 06:19.600
Come on.

06:19.830 --> 06:21.720
My problem hasn't been resolved yet.

06:21.720 --> 06:23.090
Sister Shu,

06:23.950 --> 06:26.240
there's something
I've known for a long time.

06:26.240 --> 06:28.190
I just don't know
whether I should tell you.

06:28.190 --> 06:29.000
Yes.

06:29.160 --> 06:30.690
I've recorded everything.

06:31.480 --> 06:32.690
If I show it to you,

06:32.800 --> 06:34.190
you mustn't get angry.

06:34.600 --> 06:37.730
These are all the bad things
Yu Wanyin has said about you.

06:43.000 --> 06:44.300
Yu Wanyin!

06:56.940 --> 07:00.400
[Office of Drums and Bells]

06:58.190 --> 06:58.990
You two,

06:59.390 --> 07:00.480
open the door!

07:00.630 --> 07:01.240
Your Highness,

07:01.240 --> 07:03.430
His Majesty ordered that no one may enter.

07:03.430 --> 07:05.960
A lowly discarded concubine
wants to stop me?

07:06.070 --> 07:06.830
Your Highness,

07:06.830 --> 07:08.240
please don't make things difficult for us.

07:08.240 --> 07:08.870
Stop it.

07:09.000 --> 07:10.600
You know very well the relationship

07:10.600 --> 07:11.600
between my brother and the Imperial Guard.

07:11.600 --> 07:12.260
Step aside!

07:12.600 --> 07:13.040
Oh my.

07:13.670 --> 07:15.670
Consort Shu is so efficient.

07:16.040 --> 07:17.360
I'm not even ready yet.

07:17.540 --> 07:18.140
Come here.

07:18.870 --> 07:20.680
Yu Wanyin, come out!

07:20.740 --> 07:21.480
Your Highness.

07:21.480 --> 07:22.920
Give this letter to Prince Duan

07:22.920 --> 07:24.120
and notify Eunuch An.

07:24.160 --> 07:25.000
-Yu Wanyin!
-Without my order,

07:25.000 --> 07:26.040
you must not show yourselves.

07:26.040 --> 07:27.050
-Yes, Your Highness.
-If you've got the nerve,

07:27.050 --> 07:28.180
-Go.
-open the door!

07:28.560 --> 07:29.360
Yu Wanyin!

07:29.720 --> 07:30.250
Yu Wan...

07:32.720 --> 07:33.600
Sister Shu?

07:34.000 --> 07:34.830
What brings you here?

07:34.830 --> 07:36.190
How dare you ask me that?

07:36.270 --> 07:38.070
Don't you know what you've done?

07:38.680 --> 07:40.800
I don't know. Please tell me.

07:42.000 --> 07:43.530
Two months ago you said I...

07:44.070 --> 07:44.870
What did I say?

07:45.120 --> 07:45.530
I...

07:46.310 --> 07:47.240
I said

07:47.750 --> 07:49.350
you're obsessed with novels

07:49.390 --> 07:50.600
and have the complete

07:50.600 --> 07:52.310
The Domineering Prince and Me series?

07:52.310 --> 07:53.159
Shut up!

07:53.159 --> 07:54.890
Or did I say your taste is awful,

07:55.390 --> 07:57.159
always wearing garish colors,

07:57.680 --> 07:58.540
but in reality,

07:59.040 --> 08:00.390
you can't tell red from green

08:00.390 --> 08:01.520
or blue from yellow?

08:02.510 --> 08:04.310
Or did I say that you hate bathing

08:04.310 --> 08:06.120
and cover your smell with perfume,

08:06.120 --> 08:07.980
which makes people want to vomit?

08:11.700 --> 08:12.100
You...

08:12.360 --> 08:12.680
I...

08:13.000 --> 08:13.500
I'm not!

08:15.680 --> 08:16.720
Yu Wanyin, you...

08:17.430 --> 08:18.430
Come here right now!

08:18.430 --> 08:18.890
Come...

08:19.270 --> 08:19.680
out!

08:20.720 --> 08:21.480
Yu Wanyin!

08:25.830 --> 08:27.850
I was just telling the truth,

08:28.040 --> 08:29.300
and you can't stand it?

08:30.040 --> 08:30.910
Yu Wanyin!

08:31.270 --> 08:34.200
I haven't even mentioned
all the details about how your family

08:34.200 --> 08:35.200
framed my father.

08:36.539 --> 08:40.450
[Office of Drums and Bells]

08:36.630 --> 08:37.360
Give it to me!

08:40.510 --> 08:41.840
-Yu Wanyin!
-Your Highness, please don't!

08:41.840 --> 08:43.500
Your Highness! Please don't!

08:47.000 --> 08:47.630
Yu Wanyin!

08:47.840 --> 08:50.970
By this time next year
it will be your death anniversary!

08:51.120 --> 08:53.520
She didn't grow
all that flesh for nothing.

08:54.280 --> 08:55.960
-Yu Wanyin!
-Calm down!

09:00.030 --> 09:01.120
Ganging up on me?

09:01.630 --> 09:03.630
You think I have no way to fight back?

09:03.790 --> 09:04.650
What can you do?

09:06.150 --> 09:06.840
I can run!

09:09.000 --> 09:11.000
What are you waiting for? Chase her!

09:11.440 --> 09:11.750
Let's go!

09:11.750 --> 09:12.150
Hurry!

09:15.200 --> 09:16.200
Stop right there!

09:22.750 --> 09:23.440
Don't run!

09:37.080 --> 09:37.680
Yu Wanyin!

09:37.960 --> 09:39.040
Open the door!

09:39.270 --> 09:40.070
Open the door!

09:40.600 --> 09:42.120
Haven't you eaten?

09:42.480 --> 09:43.340
Give me the axe!

09:43.910 --> 09:44.700
Move aside!

09:45.550 --> 09:47.960
His Majesty is here!

10:09.240 --> 10:10.040
Take her away.

10:10.360 --> 10:10.750
Confine her.

10:10.750 --> 10:11.960
Your Majesty, let me explain!

10:11.960 --> 10:13.020
It's not like that!

10:13.030 --> 10:13.560
Yu Wan...

10:15.360 --> 10:15.960
Your Majesty!

10:15.960 --> 10:17.030
Your Majesty, I was wrong!

10:17.030 --> 10:17.830
Your Majesty!

10:18.270 --> 10:19.870
Your Majesty, please don't!

10:20.440 --> 10:21.320
Your Majesty!

10:21.360 --> 10:21.720
CEO Dan...

10:21.720 --> 10:22.600
Your Majesty!

10:22.600 --> 10:23.360
Boss Dan!

10:24.080 --> 10:25.380
I led Consort Shu here.

10:25.510 --> 10:26.560
It was just an act.

10:26.630 --> 10:27.690
If you do this,

10:28.080 --> 10:30.000
Prince Duan
will know I didn't fall out of favor.

10:30.000 --> 10:31.120
Then all our previous performances

10:31.120 --> 10:32.110
would have been for nothing.

10:32.110 --> 10:33.670
If I don't punish her severely this time,

10:33.670 --> 10:36.510
next time someone else
will be chasing you with an axe.

10:36.510 --> 10:38.320
I'm not that unpopular.

10:38.750 --> 10:40.610
I said I would find a proper reason

10:40.790 --> 10:42.720
to bring you out of the Cold Palace.

10:42.960 --> 10:44.420
Why did you act on your own?

10:44.910 --> 10:46.240
I came in time this time.

10:46.870 --> 10:48.130
What if I'd been later?

10:48.530 --> 10:50.390
Weren't the secret guards there?

10:51.840 --> 10:52.960
I was wrong.

10:53.080 --> 10:54.750
Alright?

10:57.120 --> 10:58.720
I know you want to protect me,

10:59.600 --> 11:01.460
but I don't want your protection.

11:07.360 --> 11:08.020
Because...

11:08.780 --> 11:10.240
I want to stand by your side

11:11.200 --> 11:12.800
and fight together with you.

11:14.120 --> 11:16.230
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

11:16.550 --> 11:17.780
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

11:18.130 --> 11:20.310
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

11:20.580 --> 11:22.090
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

11:22.130 --> 11:24.470
♪ Words unspoken ♪

11:26.030 --> 11:28.480
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

11:27.960 --> 11:29.360
So how should we act next?

11:30.150 --> 11:32.300
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

11:30.790 --> 11:32.450
Does this mean you forgive me?

11:32.480 --> 11:33.640
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

11:34.110 --> 11:36.120
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

11:34.480 --> 11:36.080
I've thought it all through.

11:36.120 --> 11:36.790
We'll say

11:36.590 --> 11:37.950
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

11:37.320 --> 11:38.670
that Consort Shu
caused a scene in the Cold Palace,

11:38.050 --> 11:40.550
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

11:39.440 --> 11:40.720
and after an investigation,

11:40.720 --> 11:42.150
you realized I was truly innocent.

11:42.050 --> 11:45.390
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

11:44.080 --> 11:46.680
Then I immediately
restore your consort title

11:45.970 --> 11:49.400
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

11:47.720 --> 11:49.050
and beg you desperately

11:49.270 --> 11:50.030
to come back?

11:50.070 --> 11:53.060
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

11:50.440 --> 11:51.120
But

11:51.550 --> 11:53.240
I've already suffered so much,

11:53.240 --> 11:54.510
grown distant from you,

11:53.500 --> 11:55.400
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

11:55.390 --> 11:56.480
and my heart

11:55.630 --> 11:57.310
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

11:57.030 --> 11:58.320
is open only to Prince Duan now.

11:57.570 --> 11:59.230
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

11:59.580 --> 12:01.680
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

12:02.100 --> 12:05.250
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

12:02.120 --> 12:03.090
So

12:03.550 --> 12:05.200
I lost your foresight

12:06.120 --> 12:07.960
and could only grieve alone in sorrow.

12:06.130 --> 12:08.460
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

12:08.530 --> 12:09.680
♪ Still unchanged ♪

12:08.840 --> 12:09.640
This is called

12:09.840 --> 12:10.870
"karma for the late-blooming love"

12:10.140 --> 12:13.000
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

12:13.600 --> 12:15.050
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

12:13.840 --> 12:15.080
Then, my beloved wife,

12:15.080 --> 12:15.630
let's take

12:15.160 --> 12:22.430
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

12:16.440 --> 12:18.500
the secret passage for one last time.

12:26.470 --> 12:30.390
[Kunyu Palace]

12:45.030 --> 12:45.890
Your Highness.

12:51.000 --> 12:51.840
Consort Xie.

12:53.270 --> 12:55.870
I've brought an imperial physician
to see you.

12:56.120 --> 12:58.120
Ms. Tonghao, how thoughtful of you.

12:58.200 --> 13:01.390
Perhaps it was something
I ate for breakfast.

13:02.000 --> 13:04.270
Or maybe Consort Shu's powder

13:04.670 --> 13:05.930
had too strong a scent.

13:06.390 --> 13:07.550
But I'm fine now.

13:07.960 --> 13:08.790
In that case,

13:09.270 --> 13:11.750
you need the imperial physician
to check on you more.

13:11.750 --> 13:13.840
It will also put Her Majesty at ease.

13:25.270 --> 13:25.910
Ling,

13:26.670 --> 13:28.070
serve tea to Ms. Tonghao.

13:28.840 --> 13:29.240
Yes.

13:30.000 --> 13:30.510
No need.

13:31.390 --> 13:33.360
Once the imperial physician
has finished the examination,

13:33.360 --> 13:34.890
I need to go back and report.

13:58.790 --> 13:59.720
I deserve death!

14:00.000 --> 14:02.800
I was so clumsy.
Please forgive me, Your Highness!

14:11.110 --> 14:13.310
Physician Xiao, what's the diagnosis?

14:21.840 --> 14:24.300
Consort Xie
doesn't have a stomach problem,

14:27.480 --> 14:29.210
nor is she sensitive to smells.

14:30.630 --> 14:31.430
It's just that

14:37.320 --> 14:38.800
she didn't sleep well.

14:41.240 --> 14:43.730
Physician Xiao
said her pillow was too high,

14:44.270 --> 14:46.480
which compressed the blood vessels
in her neck

14:46.480 --> 14:49.080
and caused her dizziness and vomiting.

14:51.550 --> 14:52.870
Physician Xiao?

14:54.180 --> 14:57.450
Who is this Physician Xiao?

14:58.670 --> 14:59.960
Is he reliable?

15:00.720 --> 15:02.430
Our familiar Physician Zhang

15:02.510 --> 15:04.270
happened to be out of the palace,

15:04.270 --> 15:06.400
so I appointed a new junior physician.

15:06.840 --> 15:08.030
His position is not yet secure,

15:08.030 --> 15:09.720
so he couldn't have been bribed.

15:09.720 --> 15:11.750
Therefore, he has no reason to lie.

15:14.550 --> 15:16.440
Another false hope.

15:18.030 --> 15:19.150
I thought

15:19.600 --> 15:24.480
the Emperor
was giving me a little grandson.

15:25.500 --> 15:27.540
He's still so useless.

15:32.430 --> 15:33.510
Back then, His Majesty

15:33.510 --> 15:36.640
was traumatized
by that assassin beauty from Yan State.

15:37.390 --> 15:38.080
Perhaps

15:38.630 --> 15:40.330
since then,

15:40.870 --> 15:41.630
it has been

15:41.960 --> 15:44.420
difficult for him
to perform in the bedroom.

15:45.720 --> 15:49.240
Otherwise, it wouldn't be so difficult
to have a little Crown Prince.

15:49.240 --> 15:51.700
Difficult for him
to perform in the bedroom?

15:51.750 --> 15:53.000
That's just an act.

15:55.150 --> 15:58.550
He knew he was just a puppet.

16:00.270 --> 16:01.870
If he had disobeyed,

16:02.550 --> 16:06.150
there would have been a younger,
more obedient prince replacing him,

16:06.150 --> 16:08.720
and then he would have been useless.

16:09.240 --> 16:10.150
You mean...

16:11.360 --> 16:13.510
back then His Majesty was just pretending

16:13.510 --> 16:15.040
he had no interest in women?

16:15.320 --> 16:17.550
Whether he was pretending or not,

16:18.390 --> 16:20.720
wasn't he still at my disposal?

16:21.630 --> 16:22.630
But Your Majesty,

16:23.000 --> 16:25.260
you already had the little Crown Prince.

16:25.370 --> 16:26.030
Why

16:26.600 --> 16:27.930
did you still want more?

16:30.550 --> 16:32.280
You've been with me for so long,

16:32.670 --> 16:34.630
yet you're still so brainless.

16:40.310 --> 16:43.510
If it weren't for Xiahou Bo
keeping a covetous eye on him,

16:43.910 --> 16:45.550
how could Xiahou Dan

16:45.550 --> 16:47.670
have taken my words so seriously?

16:49.280 --> 16:50.720
Remember,

16:51.480 --> 16:53.860
never let your piece

16:53.910 --> 16:55.590
become the only

16:55.870 --> 16:57.840
irreplaceable one.

16:58.400 --> 17:00.730
Thank you for the guidance, Your Majesty.

17:02.360 --> 17:03.620
That Physician Zhang—

17:03.870 --> 17:05.270
quickly call him back

17:06.829 --> 17:08.730
to examine Consort Xie properly.

17:09.589 --> 17:10.640
I don't trust

17:11.349 --> 17:13.430
strangers.

17:13.720 --> 17:14.780
Yes, Your Majesty.

17:15.240 --> 17:16.839
I will arrange it right away.

17:28.240 --> 17:28.970
Consort Xie.

17:31.030 --> 17:31.960
Physician Xiao.

17:34.270 --> 17:35.530
Thank you for your help

17:36.640 --> 17:37.500
earlier today.

17:37.640 --> 17:38.480
Consort Xie,

17:40.000 --> 17:41.460
the fetus has just formed,

17:41.920 --> 17:43.920
and your pulse is not easy to detect.

17:45.200 --> 17:46.880
I can only help you conceal it

17:48.720 --> 17:49.590
temporarily.

18:00.550 --> 18:02.200
So it's true.

18:03.750 --> 18:06.510
Although I haven't been
in the Imperial Medical Bureau long,

18:06.510 --> 18:08.470
I know a little about the risks

18:09.030 --> 18:10.760
of being pregnant in the harem.

18:11.260 --> 18:13.790
I understand your situation,
Your Highness.

18:18.240 --> 18:19.740
Consort Xie, what are you doing?

18:19.740 --> 18:20.540
Please get up.

18:21.270 --> 18:21.730
This...

18:23.790 --> 18:24.720
Physician Xiao,

18:27.750 --> 18:28.480
this child

18:30.000 --> 18:30.860
cannot be kept.

18:35.200 --> 18:35.750
Why?

18:37.180 --> 18:39.440
Even if the Empress Dowager dislikes it,

18:39.550 --> 18:41.080
you still have His Majesty.

18:41.550 --> 18:43.750
It's precisely because of His Majesty,

18:45.480 --> 18:46.750
I cannot be pregnant

18:50.310 --> 18:51.480
if I want to survive.

18:53.720 --> 18:54.680
I dare to beg you,

18:57.590 --> 18:59.390
Physician Xiao, please save me.

19:12.440 --> 19:12.960
What?

19:13.510 --> 19:14.480
She vomited?

19:14.790 --> 19:15.440
Yes.

19:15.960 --> 19:17.680
The whole palace is talking about it.

19:17.680 --> 19:19.070
Have they found the cause of her vomiting?

19:19.070 --> 19:20.720
There are all kinds of rumors.

19:20.720 --> 19:21.680
I'm just worried

19:21.830 --> 19:22.920
that Dan's food

19:23.030 --> 19:24.490
might have been poisoned.

19:26.810 --> 19:27.810
Damn.

19:32.400 --> 19:33.800
Then this bowl of mine...

19:38.310 --> 19:39.370
Forget what I said.

19:43.310 --> 19:43.770
CEO Dan.

19:44.160 --> 19:44.620
CEO Dan.

19:44.830 --> 19:45.510
Come.

19:46.160 --> 19:46.760
Come here.

19:49.840 --> 19:51.130
Xie Yong'er vomited.

19:51.770 --> 19:53.830
Do you know what that means in a drama?

19:54.160 --> 19:54.590
What?

19:55.240 --> 19:56.170
She's pregnant.

19:56.310 --> 19:57.240
She's pregnant?

19:58.000 --> 19:58.400
She...

20:03.830 --> 20:05.170
Heaven knows,

20:05.480 --> 20:06.490
I never touched her!

20:06.490 --> 20:08.510
I've been sleeping on the floor
in the study for 2 months.

20:08.510 --> 20:09.880
My whole body hurts!

20:11.510 --> 20:12.710
Why are you laughing?

20:13.750 --> 20:14.550
Someone knows perfectly well

20:14.550 --> 20:16.150
whether I touched her or not.

20:25.110 --> 20:26.410
I was wondering

20:26.780 --> 20:28.780
why recently every time she sees me,

20:28.880 --> 20:31.960
she pounces on me like a hungry tiger.

20:33.720 --> 20:35.780
It turns out she wants to find a father

20:35.790 --> 20:37.320
for her child.

20:40.310 --> 20:40.970
Be careful.

20:44.070 --> 20:46.160
If you hadn't reminded me,
I would have forgotten.

20:46.160 --> 20:47.420
In the original story,

20:47.680 --> 20:49.480
Xie Yong'er bravely became pregnant

20:49.480 --> 20:51.310
despite pressure from the Empress Dowager

20:51.310 --> 20:52.710
and all the other powers.

20:53.400 --> 20:54.650
By the way,

20:55.070 --> 20:56.400
the child wasn't yours.

21:01.480 --> 21:02.790
This Xiahou Bo...

21:04.110 --> 21:05.170
I didn't expect him

21:06.350 --> 21:07.640
to be so...

21:08.320 --> 21:09.380
-bold.
-Reckless!

21:09.400 --> 21:12.800
-I really overestimated him!
-I really underestimated him!

21:16.350 --> 21:18.030
After all, in the original story,

21:18.030 --> 21:20.490
you, the Emperor,
were surrounded by women.

21:20.720 --> 21:22.350
Even if someone accidentally
became pregnant,

21:22.350 --> 21:23.550
she could cover it up.

21:25.240 --> 21:26.750
But our CEO Dan

21:27.680 --> 21:29.140
always keeps himself pure

21:30.480 --> 21:31.540
and never lets anyone

21:31.540 --> 21:32.310
touch him.

21:33.160 --> 21:34.510
I don't like her.

21:37.310 --> 21:38.710
I never misjudge people.

21:39.350 --> 21:41.060
You are the true gentleman,

21:41.680 --> 21:43.400
a breath of fresh air

21:43.510 --> 21:45.170
in this bloodthirsty palace.

21:48.760 --> 21:50.420
Whether I'm a gentleman or not

21:52.000 --> 21:53.330
depends on who I am with.

22:03.380 --> 22:03.980
Want some?

22:08.350 --> 22:09.210
Your Highness,

22:09.240 --> 22:11.880
earlier you ordered us to block the envoys
from entering the city.

22:11.880 --> 22:14.010
Why are you changing your position now

22:14.110 --> 22:15.550
and supporting the Emperor?

22:15.550 --> 22:16.200
Yes.

22:16.720 --> 22:18.980
Didn't you say that if the talks succeed,

22:19.070 --> 22:20.270
the border would be secure

22:20.270 --> 22:22.960
and the Empress Dowager would use
the opportunity to reclaim military power

22:22.960 --> 22:24.550
and weaken our side?

22:24.880 --> 22:26.880
Your Highness, please reconsider.

22:27.920 --> 22:29.480
The ancients said,

22:31.030 --> 22:32.550
"Plan before you act,

22:32.920 --> 22:34.580
and know when to stop to gain."

22:36.510 --> 22:37.750
But they also said,

22:39.070 --> 22:40.160
"A gentleman acts

22:41.110 --> 22:42.770
according to the situation."

22:43.160 --> 22:45.400
The Emperor of Yan came under
the pretext of birthday celebration,

22:45.400 --> 22:47.270
with the intention of negotiating.

22:47.270 --> 22:49.750
People only know the Emperor of Yan
to be weak,

22:49.750 --> 22:51.000
trying to survive

22:51.790 --> 22:53.270
through peace talks.

22:53.640 --> 22:54.920
They don't know

22:56.440 --> 22:58.700
that while the mantis stalks the cicada,

22:58.880 --> 23:00.960
the oriole is waiting behind.

23:06.790 --> 23:09.450
His Majesty
recently received a secret letter.

23:10.350 --> 23:11.830
Emperor of Yan is hospitable.

23:11.830 --> 23:13.830
I couldn't refuse his hospitality.

23:13.960 --> 23:15.550
I'm afraid I'll have to stay here
for a few days

23:15.550 --> 23:17.000
and will be late.

23:17.920 --> 23:18.590
Wang Zhao.

23:19.830 --> 23:20.550
This letter

23:21.070 --> 23:22.670
was written by Concubine Yu.

23:24.510 --> 23:26.290
So who is this Wang Zhao?

23:27.110 --> 23:27.960
Wang Zhao

23:29.270 --> 23:32.400
is the secret envoy sent by His Majesty.

23:33.070 --> 23:33.870
Could it be

23:34.970 --> 23:36.430
that these people from Yan

23:36.590 --> 23:38.190
were invited by the Emperor?

23:38.590 --> 23:40.270
You're very clever, Mr. Cao.

23:42.310 --> 23:44.070
Our puppet Emperor

23:44.330 --> 23:46.250
has finally started to resist,

23:47.110 --> 23:49.510
wanting to challenge the Empress Dowager.

23:49.550 --> 23:51.720
Based on
just one letter from Concubine Yu,

23:51.720 --> 23:53.450
are you going to believe it all?

23:53.720 --> 23:54.520
Of course not.

23:55.240 --> 23:55.770
Huixiao.

23:56.350 --> 23:56.930
I'm here.

23:57.440 --> 23:58.740
Tell everyone

23:59.720 --> 24:01.110
about what you discovered

24:01.110 --> 24:02.110
outside the city.

24:02.400 --> 24:02.850
Yes.

24:03.880 --> 24:05.780
I spied on the envoy delegation 30 li

24:05.780 --> 24:06.980
from the city at night

24:07.590 --> 24:10.240
and recognized
2 familiar faces in their group.

24:10.240 --> 24:12.300
They were Prince Tu'er's trusted men

24:12.880 --> 24:14.540
during the war with Yan State.

24:15.030 --> 24:15.960
That's strange.

24:16.510 --> 24:19.440
Tu'er has always been
at odds with the Emperor of Yan.

24:19.720 --> 24:21.980
Why would he send his men for peace talks?

24:22.350 --> 24:24.920
So this envoy delegation

24:29.510 --> 24:31.200
is a fake.

24:35.080 --> 24:42.220
[Capital of Xia]

24:51.640 --> 24:54.640
As the saying goes,
don't strike someone with a smiling face.

24:54.640 --> 24:56.580
They've traveled so far.

24:56.680 --> 24:58.640
Whether peace talks are possible or not,

24:58.640 --> 25:01.220
turning them away rudely at our gates

25:02.000 --> 25:04.480
is not how Great Xia treats guests.

25:04.480 --> 25:05.280
That's right.

25:05.640 --> 25:06.830
If word gets out,

25:07.920 --> 25:09.630
it would be embarrassing.

25:09.880 --> 25:12.200
Yesterday you said
this would disappoint the soldiers.

25:12.200 --> 25:14.590
Why today do you say
it will encourage them?

25:14.590 --> 25:17.000
No principles.
You are unfit to be a minister.

25:17.000 --> 25:17.800
Your Majesty,

25:18.070 --> 25:20.640
the Yan people are cunning and
treacherous. We must be cautious.

25:20.640 --> 25:23.170
At most,
we can let them camp outside the city.

25:23.270 --> 25:24.720
They came to congratulate His Majesty

25:24.720 --> 25:26.540
on his birthday,

25:26.640 --> 25:28.700
yet you make malicious assumptions.

25:28.960 --> 25:31.940
Your Majesty,
you must not listen to such slander!

25:32.110 --> 25:32.680
I

25:33.030 --> 25:34.890
am willing to die for my position!

25:34.920 --> 25:37.050
I too am willing to die for my position!

25:37.160 --> 25:39.290
I too am willing to die for my position!

25:39.550 --> 25:41.350
As if you're the only ones willing to die
for your position.

25:41.350 --> 25:41.720
I

25:42.440 --> 25:44.570
am also willing to die for my position!

25:44.590 --> 25:47.310
I too am willing to die for my position!

25:48.590 --> 25:49.650
What are you doing?

25:56.270 --> 25:59.160
All the civil and military officials
made valid points.

25:59.160 --> 25:59.680
I

26:01.550 --> 26:03.150
find it difficult to decide.

26:05.240 --> 26:06.770
Brother, what do you think?

26:10.510 --> 26:15.430
[Peace and Prosperity]

26:11.640 --> 26:13.720
The Yan State sent envoys to negotiate.

26:13.720 --> 26:15.310
At this auspicious moment,

26:15.790 --> 26:17.650
we should end the suffering of war

26:18.070 --> 26:19.750
and celebrate peace.

26:20.500 --> 26:22.590
Let it be done!

26:20.580 --> 26:24.650
[Peace and Prosperity]

26:26.660 --> 26:28.270
They say the Yan people
have 3 heads and 6 arms,

26:28.270 --> 26:30.200
but they seem quite ordinary to me.

26:30.200 --> 26:31.870
They do look different from us.

26:31.870 --> 26:33.130
Their eyes are sunken.

26:33.350 --> 26:34.640
Those are the envoys from Yan State?

26:34.640 --> 26:35.640
They are so strong.

26:35.640 --> 26:36.170
Make way!

26:36.640 --> 26:37.200
Everyone, make way!

26:37.200 --> 26:37.920
Make way!

26:37.920 --> 26:38.640
I told you so.

26:38.640 --> 26:39.160
Move aside!

26:39.160 --> 26:41.290
They really do look different from us.

26:41.440 --> 26:42.640
Look at their beards.

26:42.750 --> 26:44.360
I heard it was Prince Duan

26:44.400 --> 26:46.960
who suggested His Majesty
welcome the delegation into the city.

26:46.960 --> 26:48.090
You're all useless!

26:48.830 --> 26:51.840
With so many of you,
you couldn't stop one delegation

26:52.390 --> 26:55.400
and actually let them
march into the palace with impunity?

26:55.400 --> 26:56.730
And now I'm expected

26:56.830 --> 26:59.830
to dress up and entertain them
with food and drink!

27:00.370 --> 27:01.920
Empress Dowager, please calm your anger!

27:01.920 --> 27:03.590
Prince Duan suddenly changed his attitude.

27:03.590 --> 27:04.070
We...

27:04.920 --> 27:06.670
We didn't expect that.

27:07.830 --> 27:09.200
And this time, His Majesty

27:09.200 --> 27:11.800
abandoned his usual habit
of procrastination

27:12.100 --> 27:13.830
and approved it right in court.

27:14.830 --> 27:15.630
Your Majesty,

27:16.830 --> 27:18.440
the guards at the city gate

27:19.070 --> 27:20.330
are Prince Duan's men.

27:21.200 --> 27:22.600
Almost simultaneously,

27:22.860 --> 27:23.720
the gate opened

27:24.000 --> 27:26.110
and the envoy delegation was welcomed in.

27:26.110 --> 27:28.350
If you say His Majesty and Prince Duan
didn't plan this together,

27:28.350 --> 27:29.810
I simply don't believe it.

27:35.200 --> 27:36.070
You mean...

27:38.200 --> 27:38.860
Prince Duan

27:39.200 --> 27:41.200
has joined forces with the Emperor?

27:46.980 --> 27:47.710
Impossible.

27:49.440 --> 27:51.240
That's absolutely impossible.

27:52.510 --> 27:53.240
Impossible!

27:54.350 --> 27:56.150
Their resentment runs too deep.

27:57.310 --> 27:59.830
It has reached the point of life or death.

28:00.510 --> 28:01.310
Your Majesty,

28:02.110 --> 28:02.960
I believe

28:03.590 --> 28:06.050
instead of blindly guessing their motives,

28:06.240 --> 28:08.500
it's better to nip the outcome in the bud.

28:08.510 --> 28:11.240
As the saying goes,
it's better to remove the fire

28:11.400 --> 28:14.000
from under the pot
than just to pour water on it.

28:16.770 --> 28:17.900
Mr. Mu is right.

28:18.550 --> 28:20.640
These two little brats

28:20.960 --> 28:25.360
are using all their tricks
to play games with me.

28:27.140 --> 28:29.070
They want peace talks, don't they?

28:30.110 --> 28:30.840
Fine.

28:31.310 --> 28:34.950
I'll make the peace talks
end in complete disaster!

28:43.590 --> 28:44.450
Your Highness,

28:44.790 --> 28:46.550
Consort Xie sent a message,

28:47.310 --> 28:48.440
saying it's urgent.

28:52.640 --> 28:54.900
Consort Yu has just left the Cold Palace,

28:56.160 --> 28:58.220
and she's already getting restless.

28:59.390 --> 29:01.710
Women's minds are really troublesome.

29:02.510 --> 29:04.640
The maid who delivered the letter said

29:06.270 --> 29:07.830
it's about the child.

29:10.750 --> 29:11.480
The child?

29:16.750 --> 29:18.950
Didn't everyone already know about her

29:19.880 --> 29:22.340
vomiting in the Empress Dowager's chamber?

29:23.790 --> 29:26.050
This pregnancy can't be hidden anymore.

29:26.710 --> 29:28.720
But it gives us another bargaining chip.

29:28.720 --> 29:31.450
Let the Empress Dowager
and Emperor fight it out.

29:31.750 --> 29:32.880
What's the rush?

29:34.460 --> 29:36.180
[Bo, The Emperor and I were never
intimate. This child cannot be kept.]

29:34.640 --> 29:36.200
The Emperor and I were never intimate.

29:36.200 --> 29:37.750
[Please help me find a way
to have an abortion. Yong'er]

29:36.720 --> 29:38.180
This child cannot be kept.

29:38.480 --> 29:40.510
Please help me find a way
to have an abortion.

29:40.510 --> 29:41.510
This Xie Yong'er!

29:43.150 --> 29:45.150
She kept something this big from me!

29:47.240 --> 29:48.570
Your Highness, it's me.

29:49.030 --> 29:49.630
What is it?

29:55.720 --> 29:57.380
Has the letter to His Highness

29:57.790 --> 29:58.590
been sent?

29:59.350 --> 30:00.010
Yes, it has.

30:00.070 --> 30:01.400
Physician Xiao is here.

30:10.350 --> 30:11.840
Greetings, Consort Xie.

30:12.640 --> 30:13.590
Physician Xiao,

30:14.350 --> 30:16.610
didn't you already refuse me yesterday?

30:17.440 --> 30:18.440
Are you here today

30:20.240 --> 30:21.640
just to mock me?

30:22.720 --> 30:24.650
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

30:25.030 --> 30:28.790
Every step in the Imperial Medical Bureau,
from writing the prescription,

30:28.790 --> 30:31.640
preparing the medicine, to decocting it,
is carefully recorded.

30:31.640 --> 30:33.770
Each stage is monitored and reviewed.

30:34.310 --> 30:37.440
Abortion medicine
is extremely sensitive in the harem.

30:39.240 --> 30:40.570
Even if I wanted to help,

30:41.310 --> 30:42.370
I simply couldn't.

30:46.590 --> 30:49.520
Physician Xiao,
you made yourself clear yesterday.

30:49.590 --> 30:50.830
Why bother

30:52.920 --> 30:54.120
repeating yourself?

30:54.790 --> 30:57.450
Do you truly not want this child,
Your Highness?

30:59.790 --> 31:01.920
What woman doesn't long to be a mother,

31:03.000 --> 31:05.460
to safely deliver
and raise a healthy child?

31:09.030 --> 31:10.690
But as someone in the harem...

31:14.030 --> 31:15.880
I can't even control my own fate,

31:18.590 --> 31:19.920
let alone a child's.

31:33.110 --> 31:34.570
If he comes into this world

31:36.600 --> 31:37.930
without being blessed,

31:43.310 --> 31:44.640
only to become

31:45.070 --> 31:47.000
a tool in others' power struggles,

31:48.000 --> 31:48.790
to be used,

31:50.030 --> 31:52.510
bullied, oppressed, and persecuted,

31:55.830 --> 31:56.680
I would rather

32:01.590 --> 32:02.920
he never existed at all.

32:08.720 --> 32:10.520
Since you have made up your mind,

32:12.720 --> 32:13.200
I...

32:14.590 --> 32:15.480
will do my best.

32:28.560 --> 32:30.830
I've prepared two prescriptions overnight.

32:30.830 --> 32:32.470
One for calming nerves and aiding sleep,

32:32.470 --> 32:34.470
and one for improving circulation.

32:34.790 --> 32:36.200
Looking at each prescription individually,

32:36.200 --> 32:37.860
there's nothing suspicious.

32:37.920 --> 32:38.750
And they're both suitable for

32:38.750 --> 32:41.410
the condition
I diagnosed you with previously.

32:41.670 --> 32:43.270
However, if taken together,

32:43.400 --> 32:45.000
their effects will conflict

32:45.000 --> 32:47.600
and become quite similar
to an abortifacient.

32:51.440 --> 32:52.440
It's just that...

32:59.820 --> 33:00.470
What?

33:01.270 --> 33:02.520
I feel guilty.

33:03.550 --> 33:06.350
Although I've repeatedly
adjusted this medicine

33:06.400 --> 33:08.200
to make it as gentle as possible,

33:08.640 --> 33:10.770
it's still not a conventional method.

33:11.720 --> 33:13.120
It's impossible to avoid

33:13.390 --> 33:15.720
the physical harm caused by miscarriage.

33:18.360 --> 33:19.220
That's enough.

33:23.420 --> 33:25.270
Physician Xiao,
you're risking yourself to help me.

33:25.270 --> 33:26.270
I'll never forget

33:26.550 --> 33:27.750
your great kindness.

33:27.920 --> 33:29.250
I only hope that one day,

33:29.730 --> 33:30.200
I

33:32.040 --> 33:33.500
might be of service to you.

33:36.570 --> 33:38.900
Your Highness, you don't need to say that.

33:39.940 --> 33:41.540
Your Highness, please rise.

33:50.810 --> 33:53.030
This medicine
must be taken for 3 consecutive days

33:53.030 --> 33:53.890
to take effect.

33:56.000 --> 33:57.510
During this time,
you must not drink alcohol

33:57.510 --> 33:59.110
or take any other medicines.

33:59.580 --> 34:01.070
When walking or lying down,

34:01.070 --> 34:02.870
you must move gently and slowly.

34:10.400 --> 34:13.860
Please follow these instructions
carefully, Your Highness.

34:18.960 --> 34:20.090
It needs three days?

34:22.400 --> 34:23.659
Can it work any faster?

34:23.659 --> 34:26.440
Medicines that work immediately
are extremely dangerous.

34:26.440 --> 34:27.300
Your Highness,

34:27.760 --> 34:28.980
you mustn't try them.

34:59.400 --> 35:01.760
Zhang San's Diary.

35:14.880 --> 35:15.710
Dan,

35:16.840 --> 35:18.700
you haven't been to

35:18.880 --> 35:20.880
the Imperial Study for half a month.

35:20.890 --> 35:23.960
The whole palace is buzzing with gossip,

35:24.800 --> 35:27.190
saying you not only dislike studying,

35:27.710 --> 35:29.330
but also try every means

35:29.550 --> 35:31.280
to humiliate your classmates.

35:32.400 --> 35:33.930
What's the reason for this?

35:34.320 --> 35:35.730
If this continues,

35:36.440 --> 35:39.000
even I won't be able
to back you up anymore.

35:40.960 --> 35:42.820
Who was really humiliating them?

35:44.280 --> 35:46.670
You should know that better than I do.

35:47.550 --> 35:48.810
Then tell me,

35:49.590 --> 35:50.990
and I'll stand up for you.

35:55.000 --> 35:56.190
Who else could it be?

36:00.150 --> 36:02.460
I treat you like my own child!

36:00.390 --> 36:01.630
[To Father]

36:05.190 --> 36:06.240
Who wrote this?

36:07.190 --> 36:08.620
Did you write this?

36:09.150 --> 36:11.150
How dare you write a letter secretly

36:11.280 --> 36:14.080
to your father
with false accusations against me!

36:14.550 --> 36:17.280
You disappointed me completely.

36:19.030 --> 36:20.670
Has all my love and care for you

36:20.670 --> 36:22.470
all these years

36:23.070 --> 36:23.840
been

36:25.590 --> 36:26.840
for nothing?

36:28.840 --> 36:30.240
Father is the Emperor!

36:36.670 --> 36:37.510
The Emperor?

36:40.590 --> 36:41.990
He's the Emperor, right?

36:47.800 --> 36:48.690
Go and ask.

36:49.440 --> 36:50.700
In our court and harem,

36:51.400 --> 36:52.750
which Emperor

36:53.230 --> 36:54.960
has ever really been in charge?

36:54.960 --> 36:55.920
Child,

36:56.800 --> 36:58.110
wake up.

37:00.480 --> 37:01.480
I

37:04.000 --> 37:05.590
won't hide it from you.

37:07.440 --> 37:09.110
In my entire life,

37:10.110 --> 37:11.490
I've hated many people.

37:13.320 --> 37:14.320
The one I hate most

37:16.030 --> 37:17.400
is your father.

37:19.960 --> 37:20.560
But...

37:22.070 --> 37:23.410
he's about to die.

37:26.110 --> 37:26.510
You...

37:28.400 --> 37:29.600
What did you do to him?

37:35.190 --> 37:35.840
Look.

37:36.920 --> 37:38.350
This little face.

37:39.000 --> 37:40.540
When you're angry,

37:41.230 --> 37:43.400
you look just like your father.

37:45.590 --> 37:46.290
Dan,

37:47.920 --> 37:49.150
listen to me.

37:50.590 --> 37:51.640
If you

37:52.630 --> 37:55.590
don't want to stand with me,

37:56.670 --> 37:58.340
there are other princes.

38:01.760 --> 38:02.190
No.

38:03.550 --> 38:05.380
I mean other crown princes!

38:13.710 --> 38:14.210
Mother!

38:15.670 --> 38:16.270
Mother!

38:18.280 --> 38:19.240
I was wrong!

38:20.000 --> 38:21.130
I've been unfilial!

38:21.320 --> 38:23.800
I've failed your kindness.

38:24.590 --> 38:25.660
I beg you for mercy

38:26.480 --> 38:27.880
and spare my life!

38:32.110 --> 38:33.420
Alright.

38:34.070 --> 38:35.400
If you know you're wrong,

38:35.400 --> 38:37.280
just don't do it again.

38:38.230 --> 38:39.320
But Dan,

38:39.760 --> 38:41.510
let me remind you,

38:42.190 --> 38:43.630
don't try

38:44.320 --> 38:45.860
to go against me.

38:47.280 --> 38:49.110
You haven't even seen

38:50.030 --> 38:51.630
the love I have for you yet.
